Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.50,0:00:09.74,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.11,0:00:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Avrora?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.25,0:00:18.27,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,Senpai, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.42,0:00:19.50,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Ah, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.05,0:00:22.12,Default,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Come on, Kojou-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.52,0:00:25.40,Default,Nagisa,0,0,0,,You can't stare at December-san like that just because she's pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.67,0:00:27.25,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,It's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.35,0:00:31.60,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,It looks like my sister caused some trouble for you. Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.00,0:00:33.22,Default,December,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.52,0:00:35.87,Default,December,0,0,0,,If it's for a cute girl's sake, I'm more than happy to lend a hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.15,0:00:39.10,Default,December,0,0,0,,It's so peaceful, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.15,0:00:44.47,Default,December,0,0,0,,Even though terrorists set off an explosion, the shops are still selling food as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.77,0:00:46.32,Default,December,0,0,0,,And there are people who eat that food.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.07,0:00:50.42,Default,December,0,0,0,,I feel that food is directly linked to peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.60,0:00:52.47,Default,December,0,0,0,,Don't you think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.17,0:00:54.02,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.75,0:00:58.15,Default,December,0,0,0,,Bye, Nagisa-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.60,0:00:59.85,Default,December,0,0,0,,You too, Kojou-kun. Bye bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.65,0:01:04.70,Default,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Ah, Kojou-kun. What about the milk?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.10,0:01:07.00,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Sorry, I haven't looked for it yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.15,0:01:10.65,Default,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Geez, I thought you said you were going to buy some. 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.05,0:01:13.15,Default,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Ah, that shop might have some.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.30,0:01:14.60,Default,Nagisa,0,0,0,,I'll go take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.90,0:01:18.90,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Somehow, it feels like Nagisa is back to her usual self.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.27,0:01:20.92,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,Yes, that's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.02,0:01:24.15,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Food is peace, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.77,0:01:30.90,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is a terrorist attack. They are planning to throw Itogami Island into chaos and destroy it. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.32,0:01:34.85,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Tartarus Lapus's next target...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.15,0:01:35.72,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.85,0:01:37.60,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,That's what December said.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.37,0:01:41.27,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,She said that food is directly linked to peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.87,0:01:46.40,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,If Tartarus Lapus is looking to throw Itogami Island into chaos...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.05,0:01:49.10,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.35,0:01:52.37,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,It's just a guess. But I have a bad feeling about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.90,0:01:54.62,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Their next target is...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.12,0:01:59.20,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,The Great Pile on Island East. The large-scale food stockpile warehouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.12,0:01:59.20,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,{OP}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.75,0:03:40.82,Default,Senga,0,0,0,,I'm surprised you knew I was here, Minamiya Natsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.45,0:03:45.92,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,One of my students is very good at finding people.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.15,0:03:50.42,Default,Senga,0,0,0,,What has it been, fifteen years? You haven't changed a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.82,0:03:53.52,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,You're showing your age, Senga Takehito.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.50,0:03:56.97,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Are you still using children for your schemes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.72,0:04:01.22,Default,Senga,0,0,0,,I merely showed them how to use their powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.12,0:04:04.20,Default,Senga,0,0,0,,Just like you did, all those years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.57,0:04:09.30,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Are you saying that the children wish for the destruction of the Demon Sanctuary?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.55,0:04:14.05,Default,Senga,0,0,0,,I am not the leader of Tartaru Lapus, that should be proof enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.50,0:04:16.55,Default,Senga,0,0,0,,The one giving them orders is someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.75,0:04:18.97,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Oh? That's interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.22,0:04:23.30,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,But for now, destroying the Eight Trigams formation that you set up comes first.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.12,0:04:26.00,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I will listen to your explanation after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.67,0:04:35.55,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,It gets pretty chilly after sunset, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.90,0:04:39.07,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,Yes. Good thing I brought a coat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.70,0:04:40.70,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,So beautiful. 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.15,0:04:44.30,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,It's a fresh look, and I don't get tired of looking at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.52,0:04:48.02,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,S-Senpai! What are you saying, all of a sudden!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.60,0:04:50.77,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Oh, do you not like it that much, Himeragi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.02,0:04:56.42,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,No, I do like it... And besides, Nagisa-chan picked it out for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.87,0:04:58.47,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Huh? What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.65,0:05:01.17,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,Ehh? What were {\i1}you{\i0} talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.52,0:05:07.25,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Well... This area was rebuilt recently, so I thought that the view at night looked fresh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.57,0:05:09.50,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,T-The view?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.95,0:05:12.87,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,Oh, I see. I should have known.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.35,0:05:16.40,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,But Senpai, aren't you the reason why they had to rebuild it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.40,0:05:21.65,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,You couldn't control your familiar, and razed everything to the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.20,0:05:26.75,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,It wasn't my fault! That was before I got to suck your blood, Himeragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.92,0:05:28.40,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.30,0:05:34.40,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,Now it's not just me, it looks like you've sucked the blood from several other girls as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.57,0:05:39.77,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Hang on! Why did you pull your spear out after saying that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.65,0:05:43.97,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,What the hell is this incredible magical power?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.35,0:05:54.27,Default,Senga,0,0,0,,You can't stop the Roses of Tartaros the way you are now, Minamiya Natsuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.85,0:05:55.92,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,You fiend!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.42,0:05:59.72,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,Golems that control storms and waves!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.35,0:06:02.17,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,Don't tell me... Stone Soldiers?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.50,0:06:06.10,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Come out! Al-Nasl-Minium!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.82,0:06:17.17,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,It's regenerating? Dammit, this will never end!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.67,0:06:23.95,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,I will defeat the person controlling them. Senpai, please stay here and buy me some time!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.02,0:06:25.22,Default,December,0,0,0,,Sorry, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.67,0:06:28.10,Default,December,0,0,0,,I can't really let you do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.80,0:06:30.42,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,December-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.12,0:06:38.72,Default,Senga,0,0,0,,I'll leave the rest to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.47,0:06:46.77,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,You... Are you a member of Tartaros Lapus?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.00,0:06:50.22,Default,December,0,0,0,,A member? That sounds pretty nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.82,0:06:53.30,Default,December,0,0,0,,I'm actually the leader, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.50,0:06:57.02,Default,December,0,0,0,,The Fourth Primogenitor, Akatsuki Kojou.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.52,0:07:00.00,Default,December,0,0,0,,What do you say, do you want to join us?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.27,0:07:01.87,Default,December,0,0,0,,The person next to you is welcome as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.02,0:07:02.92,Default,December,0,0,0,,Like hell I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.05,0:07:04.75,Default,December,0,0,0,,Really? How unfortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.05,0:07:11.00,Default,December,0,0,0,,A D-Type!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.10,0:07:13.80,Default,December,0,0,0,,Dammit... Al-Nasl-Minium!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.40,0:07:19.30,Default,December,0,0,0,,Retreat, Al-Nasl-Minium!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.40,0:07:24.37,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,Senpai! What just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.50,0:07:26.42,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.30,0:07:48.70,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,You actually took control of the Fourth Primogenitor's mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.72,0:07:50.95,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Just who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.92,0:07:53.57,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,Mind control...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.05,0:07:56.97,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Forget about Akatsuki Kojou's familiar, transfer student.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.52,0:07:59.52,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Your opponent is that girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.17,0:08:07.90,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,I, Sword Shaman of the High God and priestess of the Lion, beseech thee.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.45,0:08:14.80,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,Spirit wolf of snowy mist, fashion a shield from the echoes of the thousand swift ones, and expel this calamity!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.07,0:08:31.05,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,Senpai! 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.40,0:08:34.10,Default,December,0,0,0,,Looks like it wore off.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.75,0:08:38.25,Default,December,0,0,0,,No matter. We have already achieved our goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.40,0:08:40.55,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Achieved your goal?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.97,0:08:50.55,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Flame control... A Pyrokinesist?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.65,0:08:54.52,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,That must be the one who caused the explosion at the Keystone Gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.97,0:08:59.70,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,So both you and Senga's Stone Soldiers... were just a distraction?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.00,0:09:04.65,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I won't let you go any further!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.30,0:09:09.75,Default,December,0,0,0,,Ugh, what's a girl got to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.35,0:09:14.37,Default,December,0,0,0,,I really didn't want to hurt Takehito's friend, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.12,0:09:16.52,Default,December,0,0,0,,Carly, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.87,0:09:24.12,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,A magical bullet?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.52,0:09:29.37,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Natsuki-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.47,0:09:30.62,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,Minamiya-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.22,0:09:33.92,Default,December,0,0,0,,Let me ask you one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.12,0:09:37.27,Default,December,0,0,0,,Akatsuki Kojou, join us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.82,0:09:41.80,Default,December,0,0,0,,You really think I'll agree, after what you just did!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.40,0:09:43.80,Default,December,0,0,0,,The Banquet of Change...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.02,0:09:50.87,Default,December,0,0,0,,Just like us, you had your fate controlled by people who wanted power.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.65,0:09:54.32,Default,December,0,0,0,,I really thought that you would understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.57,0:09:57.42,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,You... What do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.90,0:10:01.97,Default,December,0,0,0,,It looks like some of your memories are still missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.70,0:10:04.20,Default,December,0,0,0,,In that case, I'll take you by force!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.95,0:10:08.55,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Come out, Natra-Cinereus!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.47,0:10:20.00,Default,December,0,0,0,,He used a smoke screen?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.62,0:10:22.95,Default,December,0,0,0,,As expected of the boy that she picked.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.05,0:10:26.10,Default,December,0,0,0,,Time to retreat, Rogi, Carly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.42,0:10:28.27,Default,December,0,0,0,,The Roses are ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.32,0:10:37.57,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Hey, Nina.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.25,0:10:44.40,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,She got hit really hard... do you think Natsuki-chan's real body is still safe inside the Prison Barrier? 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.72,0:10:47.67,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,Well, her real body is probably unhurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.10,0:10:50.57,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,But with her Spirit Container in such a state...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.80,0:10:53.30,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,The impact of the destruction was probably transmitted to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.00,0:10:57.67,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,It might take a while until she is able to move around out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.07,0:10:58.95,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.47,0:11:03.45,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Astarte, did Natsuki-chan leave any instructions?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.32,0:11:07.52,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,One matching entry found.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.45,0:11:12.17,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,"Find out more about Tartarus's Roses."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.37,0:11:13.90,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Tartaros's Roses?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.52,0:11:15.97,Default,Kanon,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.02,0:11:23.10,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Thanks, Kanase.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.42,0:11:25.40,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,Sorry for not helping out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.60,0:11:29.32,Default,Kanon,0,0,0,,It's okay... Doing something helped me take my mind off things.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.77,0:11:31.52,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,Don't be shy, eat up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.54,0:11:37.00,SIGNS,SIGNS,0,0,0,,{\pos(627,472)}Serious food shortages expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.22,0:11:37.17,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,There's no telling how long this island will still have food left to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.30,0:11:49.70,Default,Asagi,0,0,0,,If they were canceling school, I wish they'd let me know earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.15,0:11:52.92,Default,Asagi,0,0,0,,I basically stayed up all night and still forced myself to wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.20,0:11:56.80,Default,Mogwai,0,0,0,,The island administration is in chaos, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.12,0:12:02.52,Default,Mogwai,0,0,0,,The teachers at school must also be...Oh, hang on. You have a message from Kojou.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.02,0:12:07.02,Default,Mogwai,0,0,0,,He wants you to look up something called "Tartaros's Roses".
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.95,0:12:10.67,Default,Asagi,0,0,0,,And here I thought he was actually worried about me for once.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.45,0:12:14.30,Default,Asagi,0,0,0,,What does that idiot think I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.80,0:12:17.00,Default,Mogwai,0,0,0,,It's your fault for expecting anything from him, Missy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.10,0:12:18.22,Default,Asagi,0,0,0,,Oh, shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.72,0:12:22.05,Default,Asagi,0,0,0,,Anyway, you just looked it up, right? Find anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.22,0:12:25.12,Default,Mogwai,0,0,0,,I didn't find anything of note in the company archives.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.77,0:12:30.52,Default,Mogwai,0,0,0,,I can try digging deeper in other information agencies, but that's going to take some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.72,0:12:35.70,Default,Asagi,0,0,0,,Seriously... Let Kojou know that I'll need more time to find something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.10,0:12:41.85,Default,Asagi,0,0,0,,Also, tell him that I'm going over to Motoki's house to check up on him, and if he has the time, he should come too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.90,0:12:42.75,Default,Mogwai,0,0,0,,You got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.80,0:12:48.22,Default,Asagi,0,0,0,,That person is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.50,0:12:50.87,Default,Mogwai,0,0,0,,Are you here to see Motoki?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.70,0:12:54.50,Default,Mogwai,0,0,0,,You're his senior from school, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.07,0:13:02.80,Default,Mogwai,0,0,0,,I-It's not what you think!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.90,0:13:07.50,Default,Mogwai,0,0,0,,He's just my childhood friend, and there's already someone else that I like!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.20,0:13:10.05,Default,Mogwai,0,0,0,,Gosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.82,0:13:13.97,Default,Mogwai,0,0,0,,Woah, she totally has the wrong idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.87,0:13:18.65,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,I have a bad feeling about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.52,0:13:21.65,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,It's like the calm before the storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.15,0:13:24.70,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Everything is so tense.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.77,0:13:27.02,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,I'm to blame.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.00,0:13:30.90,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,It's because I wasn't able to protect the Great Pile.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.07,0:13:33.32,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Hang on, that doesn't make sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.52,0:13:36.32,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Protecting the warehouse isn't your job, Himeragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.55,0:13:39.85,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,But I'm a Sword Shaman from the Lion King Organization...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.67,0:13:42.75,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,A {\i1}trainee{\i0} Sword Shaman, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.67,0:13:47.12,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,Umm, S-Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.97,0:13:59.02,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Do you remember the story I told you about how I messed up  during a basketball match?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.32,0:14:00.05,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.40,0:14:04.70,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,That memory flashed through my head when December hijacked my familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.25,0:14:09.22,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,I got carried away because people called me the strongest vampire in the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.48,0:14:10.68,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,And you saw how that turned out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.80,0:14:13.34,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,But that was outside your control!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.05,0:14:16.85,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,I understand how you feel, Himeragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.37,0:14:19.68,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,But sitting around moping will get us nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.74,0:14:23.20,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,We'll aim for the next time they strike.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.40,0:14:26.97,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,This is my fight now, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.80,0:14:31.08,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,No, Senpai. It's ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.45,0:14:38.88,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Still...I wonder who she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.68,0:14:41.40,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,That girl called December.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.37,0:14:47.34,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Every time I see her, I feel like my heart is being ripped apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.62,0:15:00.20,Default,Rogi,0,0,0,,If you want to know more about December, come and hang out with us for a bit, Fourth Primogenitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.80,0:15:03.34,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,You're... the one who blew up the warehouse yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.05,0:15:06.34,Default,Rogi,0,0,0,,You can call me Rogi, Akatsuki Kojou.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.22,0:15:11.05,Default,Rogi,0,0,0,,Our teacher, Senga Takehito, wants to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.31,0:15:12.22,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.77,0:15:17.17,Default,Rogi,0,0,0,,Just so you know, Carly, our sniper, has you in her sights.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.91,0:15:21.28,Default,Rogi,0,0,0,,It would be terrible if some unrelated person was hit by a stray bullet, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.54,0:15:26.68,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Where should I go?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.80,0:15:27.91,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,Senpai!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.71,0:15:30.00,Default,Rogi,0,0,0,,You'll find out soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.60,0:15:33.88,Default,Rogi,0,0,0,,We can't do much in the way of welcoming guests, so don't get your hopes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.62,0:15:47.94,Default,Senga,0,0,0,,The Fourth Primogenitor! Thanks for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.28,0:15:49.94,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,So you're Senga Takehito?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.11,0:15:50.91,Default,Senga,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.17,0:15:54.48,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,You're the one who used Feng Shui to seal off the Itogami Island?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.05,0:15:57.77,Default,Senga,0,0,0,,Well, that is my job after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.77,0:16:01.31,Default,Senga,0,0,0,,That's Ran. One of our comrades.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.05,0:16:03.57,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,It looks like they're all children.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.97,0:16:10.34,Default,Senga,0,0,0,,I don't mean this as an excuse, but I'm not forcing them to do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.94,0:16:14.25,Default,Senga,0,0,0,,They are the ones who wished for the destruction of the Demon Sanctuary.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.57,0:16:15.34,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.48,0:16:17.05,Default,Senga,0,0,0,,Take Rogi, for example.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.20,0:16:22.34,Default,Senga,0,0,0,,He is a military-use homonculus, an experimental body with the powers of pyrokinesis.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.48,0:16:23.68,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,An experimental body!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.82,0:16:25.88,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,But research on living organisms for military use is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.20,0:16:27.68,Default,Senga,0,0,0,,It is illegal, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.00,0:16:32.94,Default,Senga,0,0,0,,When that came to light and he was going to be disposed of, December saved him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.11,0:16:36.82,Default,Senga,0,0,0,,From the place that used to be known as the Iroise Demon Sanctuary.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.74,0:16:41.08,Default,Senga,0,0,0,,The other children have similar backgrounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.80,0:16:44.34,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,So that's why they're trying to destroy Itogami Island?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.85,0:16:46.31,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Because it is also a Demon Sanctuary?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.45,0:16:47.68,Default,Senga,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.85,0:16:51.08,Default,Senga,0,0,0,,There is a different reason why this place was targeted.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.25,0:16:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,A reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.60,0:16:55.14,Default,Senga,0,0,0,,That is the reason why I called you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.54,0:17:00.28,Default,Senga,0,0,0,,Once you find out about that, I hoped that you might help us as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.77,0:17:04.22,Default,Asagi,0,0,0,,Look, I'm sorry, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.48,0:17:09.65,Default,Asagi,0,0,0,,I didn't expect to encounter that person here... was her name Hiina-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.60,0:17:15.20,Default,Asagi,0,0,0,,Still, she's a little strange. Bringing fruits like these when coming to visit you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.54,0:17:17.34,Default,Asagi,0,0,0,,Well, they're delicious so I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.54,0:17:18.91,Default,Motoki,0,0,0,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.22,0:17:24.00,Default,Motoki,0,0,0,,You came here because you were worried about me, so I guess I should thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.22,0:17:26.25,Default,Asagi,0,0,0,,That's right. You should be grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.88,0:17:31.08,Default,Asagi,0,0,0,,So, how's the search for your father going?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.37,0:17:32.68,Default,Motoki,0,0,0,,Still no word from them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.20,0:17:36.54,Default,Motoki,0,0,0,,There's also the matter of restoring the Great Pile. I guess they have their hands full.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.05,0:17:42.91,Default,Asagi,0,0,0,,I'm worried... Was he attacked because he's in charge of this island? 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.54,0:17:44.77,Default,Motoki,0,0,0,,Probably, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.51,0:17:48.51,Default,Motoki,0,0,0,,But there's a bunch of stuff that doesn't sit right with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.80,0:17:49.88,Default,Asagi,0,0,0,,Like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.31,0:17:52.51,Default,Asagi,0,0,0,,The person in charge of the actual administration is my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.94,0:17:57.97,Default,Asagi,0,0,0,,If their aim was to throw the island into chaos, attacking my father doesn't make a lot of sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.28,0:18:05.74,Default,Asagi,0,0,0,,Besides, if my father could be done in by an explosion of that level, he would have died dozens of times already.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.00,0:18:13.45,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Just so you know, I have no intention of helping you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.42,0:18:16.40,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,I won't be party to murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.54,0:18:22.08,Default,Senga,0,0,0,,Murder, huh? But the people who built this island are doing the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.57,0:18:24.94,Default,Senga,0,0,0,,The next tragedy that this island will cause...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.68,0:18:30.25,Default,Senga,0,0,0,,The number of victims will be on a whole different level compared to what we've done.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.71,0:18:33.22,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,The next tragedy that the island will cause...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.45,0:18:36.62,Default,Senga,0,0,0,,The true purpose of the artificial island called Itogami Island...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.77,0:18:40.42,Default,Senga,0,0,0,,It is to function as an altar for the resurrection of the Old God Cain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.20,0:18:46.71,Default,Senga,0,0,0,,The person who designed Itogami Island, Itogami Senra, wished for Cain's resurrection.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.97,0:18:54.11,Default,Senga,0,0,0,,While he is no longer alive, there are still people in Itogami Island's administration who have inherited his ideology. 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.57,0:18:59.51,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,So, the directors of the island's administration whom you assassinated...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.85,0:19:03.28,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,That's your excuse for terrorism?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.57,0:19:07.88,Default,Senga,0,0,0,,What do you say, Fourth Primogenitor? Do you feel like helping us now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.25,0:19:11.25,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Help? You can't be serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.88,0:19:14.02,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,So in the end, you're all the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.71,0:19:15.88,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.17,0:19:17.45,Default,Senga,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.45,0:19:21.88,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Why are you guys trying to take on everything by yourselves?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.74,0:19:27.48,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,I feel like I'm looking at my past self in a mirror, it's pretty embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.88,0:19:32.48,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Why didn't you ask for help? Why didn't you raise your voices?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.62,0:19:36.11,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,After going so far as to become terrorists, do you think anyone would take your side?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.20,0:19:39.11,Default,Senga,0,0,0,,Of course we raised our voices.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.37,0:19:42.62,Default,Senga,0,0,0,,But our efforts were wiped out by those with authority.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.05,0:19:49.00,Default,Senga,0,0,0,,Even when our voices reached some people, no one was willing to believe us because we had no clear proof!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.60,0:19:50.88,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Are you sure that's really true?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.42,0:19:55.17,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Was the lack of proof really why people refused to believe you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.51,0:19:56.80,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,You know that's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.05,0:19:59.74,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,It's because you guys didn't believe in anyone yourselves! 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.97,0:20:00.80,Default,Senga,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.11,0:20:04.85,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,You said a lot of people would die if Cain was resurrected, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.34,0:20:08.80,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,In that case, you shouldn't be destroying the Demon Sanctuary.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.14,0:20:11.45,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,You should be saving the people who will be sacrificed instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.77,0:20:14.17,Default,Rogi,0,0,0,,Saying whatever you want...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.28,0:20:16.68,Default,Senga,0,0,0,,Stop, Rogi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.11,0:20:21.34,Default,Senga,0,0,0,,I suppose we walk different paths, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.45,0:20:22.97,Default,Senga,0,0,0,,But that no longer matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.17,0:20:25.20,Default,Senga,0,0,0,,We have already carried out our objective.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.45,0:20:26.28,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Objective?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.82,0:20:28.91,Default,Senga,0,0,0,,We have no intention of changing our methods.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.20,0:20:33.54,Default,Senga,0,0,0,,We will take direct action to prevent the resurrection of the Old God.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.97,0:20:36.48,Default,Senga,0,0,0,,By obliterating the Priestess of Cain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.74,0:20:37.94,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Priestess of Cain?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.17,0:20:39.57,Default,Senga,0,0,0,,Were you not aware?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.97,0:20:41.45,Default,Senga,0,0,0,,Aiba Asagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.62,0:20:43.11,Default,Senga,0,0,0,,It's your friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.22,0:20:47.91,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,You called us here to separate us from Aiba-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.48,0:20:49.68,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Senga!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.48,0:20:51.42,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.51,0:20:57.82,Default,Senga,0,0,0,,I won't ask for your forgiveness, Fourth Primogenitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.25,0:20:59.51,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Feng Shui, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.82,0:21:01.68,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,Senpai, get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.82,0:21:14.40,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.40,0:21:15.05,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.54,0:21:21.94,Default,Asagi,0,0,0,,What's taking Kojou so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.28,0:21:24.22,Default,Asagi,0,0,0,,There won't be any melon left for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.42,0:21:26.68,Default,Motoki,0,0,0,,Why are you eating the whole thing-
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.71,0:21:32.82,Default,Motoki,0,0,0,,Asagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.68,0:21:34.85,Default,Asagi,0,0,0,,What was that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.94,0:21:35.71,Default,Motoki,0,0,0,,A sniper!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.11,0:21:42.71,Default,Motoki,0,0,0,,They're using explosive rounds in a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.97,0:21:44.11,Default,Motoki,0,0,0,,Are they insane?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.31,0:21:45.94,Default,Asagi,0,0,0,,What the hell is going on!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.25,0:21:49.71,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,It's no good, I can't get through!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.42,0:21:52.40,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,Senpai! Where is Yaze-senpai's house?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.71,0:21:55.31,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,From here, it is around two stops away by monorail.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.82,0:22:00.62,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Himeragi!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.85,0:22:01.77,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.45,0:22:03.88,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,S-Senpai!?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.48,0:22:12.11,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,This power is... from that sword-shaped familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.62,0:22:14.68,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,You're able to control it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.85,0:22:19.14,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,No... I don't really get it, but I felt like it would work now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.42,0:22:21.71,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,You're using the power in such an incomplete state?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.00,0:22:29.25,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.60,0:22:34.65,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.17,0:22:39.02,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,After we save Asagi, I'm never going to do something this exhausting again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.68,0:22:42.77,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,Is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.25,0:22:44.62,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Asagi must be over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.94,0:22:55.68,Default,December,0,0,0,,So you came after all, Akatsuki Kojou.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.31,0:22:58.31,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Get out of my way, December.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.85,0:23:01.88,Default,December,0,0,0,,I cannot allow Aiba Asagi to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.42,0:23:04.85,Default,December,0,0,0,,She is far too dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.17,0:23:07.65,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Come out, Regulus Aurum!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.62,0:23:11.68,Default,December,0,0,0,,Retreat, Regulus Aurum!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.17,0:23:18.62,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Come out... Come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.97,0:23:23.85,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Mesarthim-Adamas! Al-Nasl-Minium! Al-Meissa-Mercury!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.02,0:23:32.65,Default,December,0,0,0,,Retreat! Mesarthim-Adamas! Al-Nasl-Minium! Al-Meissa-Mercury!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.88,0:23:41.14,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,Senpai, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.22,0:23:44.17,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,I'll handle her, so-!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.22,0:23:46.20,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Come out, Kiffa-Ater!  
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.48,0:23:54.54,Default,December,0,0,0,,Retreat... My brethren!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.80,0:24:01.71,Default,Kojou,0,0,0,,Come out! Sadalmelik-Albus! Cor Tauri-Sucinum!!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.08,0:24:10.11,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.17,0:24:13.17,Default,December,0,0,0,,Again...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.17,0:24:20.08,Default,December,0,0,0,,Are you going to kill me once more, Akatsuki Kojou?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.20,0:24:32.42,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.97,0:24:38.00,Default,Senga,0,0,0,,You did well, December.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.14,0:24:39.57,Default,Senga,0,0,0,,That was more than enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.88,0:24:44.31,Default,Senga,0,0,0,,We're out of time, Ran. Activate the Roses.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.42,0:24:54.60,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,Senpai! Pull yourself together! Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,{ED}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,{vol 13 page 170}  
